    <div class="faq-container">
        <h1>Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)</h1>
        <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Q: What is a Funko Pop? <i id="arrow" class="fa-solid fa-caret-down"></i></h3>
            <p>A: Funko Pop figures are collectible vinyl figures of characters from various franchises, including movies, TV shows, games, and more. They are known for their oversized heads and adorable designs.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Q: Are Marvel Funko Pops limited edition? <i id="arrow" class="fa-solid fa-caret-down"></i></h3>
            <p>A: Some Marvel Funko Pops are limited edition and can only be found at specific retailers or conventions. These limited editions usually have a special sticker on the box to indicate their exclusivity.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Q: How can I ensure the authenticity of my Funko Pop? <i id="arrow" class="fa-solid fa-caret-down"></i></h3>
            <p>A: To ensure authenticity, purchase your Funko Pops from reputable retailers or directly from the Funko website. Be wary of deals that seem too good to be true, as they may be counterfeit products.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Q: How should I store my Funko Pop collection? <i id="arrow" class="fa-solid fa-caret-down"></i></h3>
            <p>A: To maintain the condition of your Funko Pops, keep them in a cool, dry place away from direct sunlight. Many collectors prefer to keep their figures in the original box to preserve their value.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Q: Can I sell or trade my Funko Pops on your website? <i id="arrow" class="fa-solid fa-caret-down"></i></h3>
        <p>A: Currently, our website does not support selling or trading Funko Pops. However, you can find many online communities and marketplaces where collectors buy, sell, and trade their figures.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Q: What types of payment do you accept?  <i id="arrow" class="fa-solid fa-caret-down"></i></h3>
            <p>A: We accept major credit cards, PayPal, and other forms of payment as detailed on our checkout page. Please refer to the payment options available when you complete your purchase.</p>
        </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Q: How long does it take to ship my order?  <i id="arrow" class="fa-solid fa-caret-down"></i></h3>
            <p>A: Shipping times vary based on your location and the shipping method chosen at checkout. Typically, orders are processed within 1-2 business days and delivered within 5-7 business days for standard shipping.</p>
        </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Q: Can I return or exchange my Funko Pop?  <i id="arrow" class="fa-solid fa-caret-down"></i></h3>
            <p>A: Yes, we offer a 30-day return policy for unopened and undamaged Funko Pops. Please visit our return policy page for instructions on initiating a return or exchange.</p>
          </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Q: Do you offer gift cards?  <i id="arrow" class="fa-solid fa-caret-down"></i></h3>
            <p>A: Yes, we offer gift cards in various denominations. You can purchase them directly from our website and they can be used for any products available on our site.</p>
          </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Q: How can I track my order?  <i id="arrow" class="fa-solid fa-caret-down"></i></h3>
            <p>A: Once your order is shipped, you will receive a confirmation email with a tracking number. Use this number to track your shipment through our shipping partner's website.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Q: Do you offer international shipping?  <i id="arrow" class="fa-solid fa-caret-down"></i></h3>
            <p>A: Yes, we do offer international shipping. Shipping fees and delivery times will vary based on the destination country. Please refer to our shipping page for more details.</p>
        </div>
